				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>On some project, it might a good thing not to clear out the grid. Meaning, keep—some of—it visible.</p>
<p>Having a thin, barely visible but there, line under each line of a long and complex text help some people to read it, and to do so faster and more easily. It might even be an Accessibility improvement.</p>
