						<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/705b835ca26c8f73a1b89659c38e7f02?s=120&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/705b835ca26c8f73a1b89659c38e7f02?s=240&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-120 photo' height='120' width='120' loading='lazy'/>						<b class="fn"><a href='http://www.thewatchmakerproject.com/' rel='external nofollow ugc' class='url'>Matthew Pennell</a></b> <span class="says">says:</span>					</div><!-- .comment-author -->

					<div class="comment-metadata">
