							<time datetime="2007-04-10T15:02:50-04:00">
								April 10, 2007 at 3:02 pm							</time>
						</a>
											</div><!-- .comment-metadata -->

									</footer><!-- .comment-meta -->

				<div class="comment-content">
					<p>Steve Marshall has used the idea of a baseline grid to good effect on a &#8220;recent redesign of his site&#8221;:<a href="http://nascentguruism.com/?show=baselines" rel="nofollow ugc">http://nascentguruism.com/?show=baselines</a> which also includes optional visible baseline and layout grids.</p>
				</div><!-- .comment-content -->

