			<article id="div-comment-11239" class="comment-body">
				<footer class="comment-meta">
					<div class="comment-author vcard">
						<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e309664a2a492f4467bf2b092ddae3a7?s=120&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/e309664a2a492f4467bf2b092ddae3a7?s=240&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-120 photo' height='120' width='120' loading='lazy'/>						<b class="fn"><a href='http://www.okupski.name/' rel='external nofollow ugc' class='url'>Cezary Okupski</a></b> <span class="says">says:</span>					</div><!-- .comment-author -->

