				<footer class="comment-meta">
					<div class="comment-author vcard">
						<img alt='' src='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/?s=120&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g' srcset='https://secure.gravatar.com/avatar/?s=240&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g 2x' class='avatar avatar-120 photo avatar-default' height='120' width='120' loading='lazy'/>						<b class="fn">Steve Dill</b> <span class="says">says:</span>					</div><!-- .comment-author -->

					<div class="comment-metadata">
