					<p>i am trying to set up a baseline grid for myself. i have to say it&#8217;s pretty easy if you take only block elements like headings and paragraphs into account, and if you don&#8217;t care if at some font-size/font-family combinations you won&#8217;t get a pixel-precise baseline grid. what really gives me headaches are forms and tables. is there any example of anybody doing this pixel-perfect?</p>
